divs: Sighting DetailsLet my dog out to go to bathroom back porch of house Notice from my left eye an orb not to bright venus or mars was brighter. The orb went west to east as usually through here. Watch it till out of site. No sound or flashing lights or running lights. Just an orb. Speed slow but consistent pace. Size of orb small. I think it was an orb I've seen on youtube when people grab their video cams. Christopher Seum Moundsvill, West Virginia 26041-1336
